<div class="nass margin-top-10"> <p><span id="p1" class="anchor"></span>التفعُّل<a href="#p1" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p2"></span><span class="c4">[م]</span><a href="#p2" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p3"></span><span class="c4">[تَثَعَّم]</span>: حكى بعضهم: تَثَعَّمَتْ فلاناً أرضُ فلان: إِذا أعجبتْه فمرَّ إِليها، من الثَّعْم، وهو النَّزْع. ورواها أبو زيد <span class="c2">«١»</span> تَنَعَّمَتْه.<a href="#p3" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p4"></span>الفَعْلَلَة<a href="#p4" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p5"></span><span class="c4">[جر]</span><a href="#p5" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p6"></span><span class="c4">[ثَعْجَر]</span> الدمَ وغيره فاثْعَنْجَر: أي صبَّه فانصبَّ.<a href="#p6" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p7"></span>الافْعِنْلال<a href="#p7" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p8"></span><span class="c4">[جر]</span><a href="#p8" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p9"></span><span class="c4">[اثْعَنْجَر]</span> الدمُ وغيرُه: انصبَّ، قال امرؤ القيس <span class="c2">«٢»</span>:<a href="#p9" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p10"></span>وجَفْنَةٍ مُدَعْثَرَهْ ... وطَعْنَةٍ مُثْعَنْجِرَهْ<a href="#p10" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
<p><span class="anchor" id="p11"></span>والنون زائدة.<a href="#p11" class="btn_tag btn btn-sm"><span class="text-gray fa fa-copy"></span></a></p>
